---
+---------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
+---------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | BytesProcessedNode                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |   Federated                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |  Sort: profit.nation ASC NULLS LAST, profit.o_year DESC NULLS FIRST                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |   Projection: profit.nation, profit.o_year, sum(profit.amount) AS sum_profit                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |     Aggregate: groupBy=[[profit.nation, profit.o_year]], aggr=[[sum(profit.amount)]]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
|               |       SubqueryAlias: profit                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |         Projection: tpch.tpch.nation.n_name AS nation, date_part(Utf8("YEAR"), tpch.tpch.orders.o_orderdate) AS o_year, tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice * (Int64(1) - tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_discount) - tpch.tpch.partsupp.ps_supplycost * tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_quantity AS amount                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
|               |           Inner Join:  Filter: tpch.tpch.supplier.s_nationkey = tpch.tpch.nation.n_nationkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |             Inner Join:  Filter: tpch.tpch.orders.o_orderkey = tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_orderkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |               Inner Join:  Filter: tpch.tpch.partsupp.ps_suppkey = tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_suppkey AND tpch.tpch.partsupp.ps_partkey = tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_partkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |                 Inner Join:  Filter: tpch.tpch.supplier.s_suppkey = tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_suppkey AND tpch.tpch.part.p_partkey = tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_partkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |                   Cross Join:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |                     Filter: tpch.tpch.part.p_name LIKE Utf8("%green%")                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |                       TableScan: tpch.tpch.part projection=[p_partkey, p_name]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |                     TableScan: tpch.tpch.supplier projection=[s_suppkey, s_nationkey]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
|               |                   TableScan: tpch.tpch.lineitem projection=[l_orderkey, l_partkey, l_suppkey, l_quantity, l_extendedprice, l_discount]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |                 TableScan: tpch.tpch.partsupp projection=[ps_partkey, ps_suppkey, ps_supplycost]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |               TableScan: tpch.tpch.orders projection=[o_orderkey, o_orderdate]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |             TableScan: tpch.tpch.nation projection=[n_nationkey, n_name]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
| physical_plan | BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |   SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
|               |     VirtualExecutionPlan name=spice.ai compute_context=url=https://flight.spiceai.io,username=,org=spiceai,app=tpch initial_sql=SELECT "profit"."nation", "profit"."o_year", sum("profit"."amount") AS "sum_profit" FROM (SELECT "nation"."n_name" AS "nation", date_part('YEAR', "orders"."o_orderdate") AS "o_year", (("lineitem"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "lineitem"."l_discount")) - ("partsupp"."ps_supplycost" * "lineitem"."l_quantity")) AS "amount" FROM "tpch"."tpch"."part" INNER JOIN "tpch"."tpch"."supplier" ON "part"."p_name" LIKE '%green%' INNER JOIN "tpch"."tpch"."lineitem" ON (("supplier"."s_suppkey" = "lineitem"."l_suppkey") AND ("part"."p_partkey" = "lineitem"."l_partkey")) INNER JOIN "tpch"."tpch"."partsupp" ON (("partsupp"."ps_suppkey" = "lineitem"."l_suppkey") AND ("partsupp"."ps_partkey" = "lineitem"."l_partkey")) INNER JOIN "tpch"."tpch"."orders" ON ("orders"."o_orderkey" = "lineitem"."l_orderkey") INNER JOIN "tpch"."tpch"."nation" ON ("supplier"."s_nationkey" = "nation"."n_nationkey")) AS "profit" GROUP BY "profit"."nation", "profit"."o_year" ORDER BY "profit"."nation" ASC NULLS LAST, "profit"."o_year" DESC NULLS FIRST rewritten_sql=SELECT "profit"."nation", "profit"."o_year", sum("profit"."amount") AS "sum_profit" FROM (SELECT "nation"."n_name" AS "nation", date_part('YEAR', "orders"."o_orderdate") AS "o_year", (("lineitem"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "lineitem"."l_discount")) - ("partsupp"."ps_supplycost" * "lineitem"."l_quantity")) AS "amount" FROM "spice"."tpch"."part" INNER JOIN "spice"."tpch"."supplier" ON "part"."p_name" LIKE '%green%' INNER JOIN "spice"."tpch"."lineitem" ON (("supplier"."s_suppkey" = "lineitem"."l_suppkey") AND ("part"."p_partkey" = "lineitem"."l_partkey")) INNER JOIN "spice"."tpch"."partsupp" ON (("partsupp"."ps_suppkey" = "lineitem"."l_suppkey") AND ("partsupp"."ps_partkey" = "lineitem"."l_partkey")) INNER JOIN "spice"."tpch"."orders" ON ("orders"."o_orderkey" = "lineitem"."l_orderkey") INNER JOIN "spice"."tpch"."nation" ON ("supplier"."s_nationkey" = "nation"."n_nationkey")) AS "profit" GROUP BY "profit"."nation", "profit"."o_year" ORDER BY "profit"."nation" ASC NULLS LAST, "profit"."o_year" DESC NULLS FIRST |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
+---------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
